{"tid":363612,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]大叔配蘿莉","createTime":"2017-08-17T18:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T18:15:00.000Z","uid":45405,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad82a7d9b3e6226bf05e51bd988870437f14354","tid":363612,"uid":45405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"一路有養開隻奶茶鼠叫喵喵，2個幾月大的男仔黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/015327_298a7dc8b1dfbe69e0a1da8b5333adbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F015327_298a7dc8b1dfbe69e0a1da8b5333adbb.jpg&h=34a8d285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見佢平日又好似好靜，打算幫佢搵下個朋友，之後就接左隻銀狐女(3個星期大，叫咪咪)返屋企。爬過文就知道奶茶同銀狐係唔可以一齊養，一定要分籠，咁抱住試一試都無壞既心態，於是就洗乾淨個籠，洗走曬喵喵d氣味，然後先放咪咪(女)入去一陣，最後再放喵喵入去。<br />\n正所謂窈窕淑女就供不應求，又可能係喵喵差唔多發情期，入左去隔左一陣，喵喵一野騎住咪咪，咪咪叫到成間房都聽到，我分開左佢地3次就騎足成次，之後決定要分籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喵喵[肥仔大叔]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/020347_84700b974d3f2e71a2d6a61f3c6578a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F020347_84700b974d3f2e71a2d6a61f3c6578a0.jpg&h=8410ccbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/020605_d7f4f8f45c08c48863d24b7d754d824f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F020605_d7f4f8f45c08c48863d24b7d754d824f.jpg&h=ebaa59db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪咪[窈窕蘿莉]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/020458_fcf32185a60acd78a79c85d9285d99be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F020458_fcf32185a60acd78a79c85d9285d99be.jpg&h=1300ae90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/020459_acb78ff119936d10f309ce2c3159a453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F020459_acb78ff119936d10f309ce2c3159a453.jpg&h=c4d98355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家將佢地分開左上下層，要保護未成年少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/020544_f8e72b36e6fb4a8e5dddbdda7aeaf8a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F020544_f8e72b36e6fb4a8e5dddbdda7aeaf8a5.jpg&h=4aa9449b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲d會買個60x50既大箱比喵喵住，等佢地可以多d空間活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c968bdaa5848a642e7fe2a97a4b21f90f548264","tid":363612,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:12:52.000Z","msg":"唔會互咬互食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37055c0390832e6279aadc420f756d32b8c1041","tid":363612,"uid":45405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會互咬互食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一半一半機會架，所以頭幾日要睇住，而家男仔係咁騎住女仔，就要快d分開佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}